description: I'm selling a 2000 javelin renegade 19 dual console, Johnson 175. It has a 2009 minnkotta trolling motor 70lb 24V and it recessed in the floor. It has original carpet , in great shape. New covered seats marine grade leather, two tone burg/tan. 3 bran new batteries, 27 series 1 optima and 2 interstate. Lowrance graphs. All storage lids are aluminum. There's no soft spots. It has retractable rod straps. I have the lean seat and rear seat with back rest. I have a full cover. Everything works great there's absolutely nothing wrong with this boat it runs good with 4 blade 60mph. And white the raker 3 blade 68mph. And it may run faster I just haven't held it wide open long.  This boat hasn't been rode hard and put up wet. I take good care of my things so they last a while it's been garage kept.  The motor runs great. I purchased this boat from competition marine in basset va. Last year and haven't burned 4 tanks of gas since I bought it. When I purchased the boat he said the motor was rebuilt never been bored just had to replace one sleeve. It has great compression I had an issue earlier this year the boat was making a clunk noise at half throttle and I took it to him , he checked it out and said my lower unit was the problem so we decided to buy a new one instead of rebuilding it. So that's new. I have 2 props both stainless 4 blade shooter and 3 blade Raker. Power trim works double live wells 2 rod storage one big lure storage and 2 big misc. storage behind both seats.  This boat is a great boat. Never has let me down or stranded just needs a new home. The reason I'm selling is I just had a little girl and I'm not going to have time to use it. And I have 3 more boats they're more of a family oriented boat. If u have any questions feel free to ask.  Oh and the trailer is included new bearings,brakes, tires ,and lights and all new wires. Not interested in trades or pay pal. Cash money!!! U want it shoot me a offer.
title: 00 JAVELIN BASS BOAT
